[select * from wkohdr_note where wkonum = @wkonum and client_id = @client_id and wkorev = @wkorev and wh_id = @wh_id]
[select * from wkodtl_note where wkonum = @wkonum and client_id = @client_id and wkorev = @wkorev and wh_id = @wh_id]
[select * from wkohdr_ins where @*]
[select * from wkodtl_ins where @*]
[select * from pckmov where exists (select 'x' from pckwrk_dtl where pckwrk_dtl.cmbcod = pckmov.cmbcod and wkonum = @wkonum and wkorev = @wkorev and client_id = @client_id and wh_id = @wh_id)]

[ select pckwrk_hdr.* from pckwrk_hdr,pckwrk_dtl where  pckwrk_hdr.wrkref = pckwrk_dtl.wrkref and pckwrk_dtl.wkonum = @wkonum and pckwrk_dtl.wkorev = @wkorev and pckwrk_dtl.client_id = @client_id and pckwrk_dtl.wh_id = @wh_id]
[select * from canpck where wkonum = @wkonum and wkorev = @wkorev and client_id = @client_id and wh_id = @wh_id]
[select * from wko_setup where wkonum = @wkonum and wkorev = @wkorev and client_id = @client_id and wh_id = @wh_id]
[select * from cmphdr where wkonum = @wkonum and wkorev = @wkorev and client_id = @client_id and wh_id = @wh_id]
[select d.* from cmpdtl d, cmphdr h where h.cmpkey = d.cmpkey and h.wkonum = @wkonum and h.wkorev = @wkorev and h.client_id = @client_id and h.wh_id = @wh_id]

[select isn.* from cmpdtl d, cmphdr h, inv_ser_num isn where h.cmpkey = d.cmpkey and (d.subnum = isn.invtid or d.dtlnum = isn.invtid)  and h.wkonum = @wkonum and h.wkorev = @wkorev and h.client_id = @client_id and h.wh_id = @wh_id]

[ select pckwrk_dtl.* from pckwrk_dtl,pckwrk_hdr where  pckwrk_hdr.wrkref = pckwrk_dtl.wrkref and pckwrk_dtl.wkonum = @wkonum and pckwrk_dtl.wkorev = @wkorev and pckwrk_dtl.client_id = @client_id and pckwrk_dtl.wh_id = @wh_id]
